services.recommendation:
Capture raw H2 DATA frame bytes to verify actual SSE wire format. Use curl --http2 or Wireshark to inspect exact bytes sent. Expected format: 'data: {"id":0,"result":{"type":"started"}}

data: {"id":0,"result":{"type":"data","data":{...}}}

data: {"id":0,"result":{"type":"stopped"}}

'. Each 'data: ' line must be on its own line with actual 0x0A bytes as delimiters.
